{"tid":237261,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打招絲打 6月中去歐遊一個月","createTime":"2017-05-10T09:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T20:27:31.000Z","uid":51860,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83bfa4f4621b584f06054c4e6fdfe301161019f2","tid":237261,"uid":51860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:18:18.000Z","msg":"有冇絲打有興趣<br />\n原本同朋友約好左，傾曬幾時出發，係今日諗住deadline買平來回機票既時候話冇錢都係唔去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預計來回機票～4000hkd<br />\n<br />\n六月中玩到七月中<br />\n<br />\n行程想去邊可以大家再討論<br />\n<br />\n有興趣加我tg：NYC999<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/NYC999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNYC999&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmer%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=804f3b41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/NYC999</a><br />\n<br />\n我係真絲，唔係扮女人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ad97fba88a3be4f3f83fca926d205d781ce4bc","tid":237261,"uid":51860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"預計可以玩5-6個國家，budget 20000鬆d<br />\n<br />\n我舊年歐遊1個月淨洗費～&euro;900歐羅（有剩），唔計機票住宿"},{"pid":"7b2a39b3377ddcac1b1f82176b357a7e1ff42710","tid":237261,"uid":67257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"你邊度買機票有咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b6f283b51fa83a60c6eeb179aee87c261796b5","tid":237261,"uid":51860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"800d79eb932648240b02eaf84886ee83bf3eb7bd","tid":237261,"uid":51860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你邊度買機票有咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n卡塔爾航空<br />\n早兩日睇<br />\n去程：hk to 伊斯坦堡<br />\n<br />\n回程：羅馬to hk<br />\n<br />\n$3606"},{"pid":"c28adaf103fa6cc64becfd1182a1eea8732c78e3","tid":23726